         <abstract id="aspace_f23a7db052e7aca40c3d7d061c89697d">The materials consist of photographs of buildings constructed for the Yale bicentennial. The bulk of the collection documents the University Dining Hall and Woolsey Hall. One photograph documents construction in 1901.</abstract>
    
